      "span_text": "To determine if there were ancillary binding sites located on gp120, as previously suggested [CITATION_1] , binding of mAbs 4E10 and 2F5 to deglycosylated HIV-1 Env 89.6 gp120 was determined using the same non-denaturing conditions as used for binding of mAbs 2F5 or 4E10 mAb binding to deglycosylated JRFL gp140.",
